    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Extremely accurate electronic clocks using the natural frequency of vibrations of quartz crystals to regulate the clock's movement.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
